</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Bestow Elements?</span><hr size=1> After seeing Clerics get the Ability &quot;Bestow Divine Aura&quot; which allows them to use an 18 second invincibility spell on any player, it got me a-thinking....<br>
<br>
How about 4 bestow spells which add to a player's effectiveness based on an element...<br>
<br>
Bestow Air<br>
Adds extra damage avoidance (extra chance of Dodge/Parry/Riposte beign successful).<br>
Adds an extra process to the character it is cast on:<br>
5 second Stun.<br>
Has the ability to stun mobs up to level 60, similar to the Paladin Class AA.<br>
Duration: 5 minutes or whatever<br>
<br>
Bestow Flame<br>
Adds +40 CR<br>
Adds a damage shield which stacks with all others.<br>
Level 1 = 25<br>
Level 2 = 50<br>
Level 3 = 100<br>
I don't know about all the other damage shields you cans tack ontop of other DS, so this figure may need adjusting, but you get the idea.<br>
<br>
Bestow Water<br>
Adds +30 to Poison/Disease<br>
Adds an Ice DD/split second stun similar to the Chaotic Feedback line of spells.<br>
<br>
Bestow Earth<br>
Adds extra damage mitigation.<br>
Snare's target.<br>
Makes target invulnerable to stun effects (melee or spell inflicted) and movement interruption.<br>
<br>
Air, Fire and Water are mainly useful for the main tank/Assistant tanks.<br>
<br>
Earth could be used for either, but would be more useful for casters. AN inctrease in the snare %age (ie: 75%) would make running casting very difficult if not impossible, but would allow a cleric class get the complete heal off more easily, especially if the MoB is beating on him/her.<br>
<br>
These ideas are evry sketchy and in need of refinement. None of the durations woudl be very long, to prevent chain AA and abuse, similar to the elemental form line. Hey, maybe add the illusion component too! That'd be funny, turn the ogre into an ickle fire elemental <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Majishia Vie <Wyrd Angles>
